 dated from ~4000 years ago to present only show ~2.7% of Botai-related ancestry. This indicates that a massive genomic turnover underpins the expansion of the horse stock that gave rise to modern domesticates, which coincides with large-scale human population expansions during the Early Bronze Age.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Gaunitz, Charleen", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fages, Antoine", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hangh\u00f8j, Kristian", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Albrechtsen, Anders", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Khan, Naveed", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schubert, Mikkel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Seguin-Orlando, Andaine", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Owens, Ivy J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Felkel, Sabine", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bignon-Lau, Olivier", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "De Barros Damgaard, Peter", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mittnik, Alissa", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mohaseb, Azadeh F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Davoudi, Hossein", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Alquraishi, Saleh", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Alfarhan, Ahmed H.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Al-Rasheid, Khaled A. S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Crub\u00e9zy, Eric", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Benecke, Norbert", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Olsen, Sandra", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Brown, Dorcas", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Anthony, David", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Massy, Ken", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pitulko, Vladimir", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kasparov, Aleksei", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Brem, Gottfried", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hofreiter, Michael", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mukhtarova, Gulmira", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Baimukhanov, Nurbol", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "L\u00f5ugas, Lembi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Onar, Vedat", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Stockhammer, Philipp W.", "affiliation"